      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This driver-focused example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Noteworthy maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe\u2014essential for long-term chassis rigidity. The suspension has been enhanced with poly-bushes and Bilstein B6 dampers for sharpened turn-in and superior damping control. The individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, ensuring immediate throttle response and that signature metallic induction howl. This is a well-sorted, honest example of a modern classic, sorted for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and handling dynamics.",
